&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with the Dev, Product, and Analytics teams to implement and successfully integrate models and capabilities into production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play a pivotal role in shaping the vision for the analytical capabilities of our core products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Constantly experiment with new ways to improve our product offering, including complex experimental design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the training of our strategic models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the research and development of core product Machine Learning capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Standardize processes and methods used within the team and group&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
