&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years experience as a team lead of a data science team, managing at least 3 ICs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years proven hands-on IC experience implementing machine learning algorithms and techniques in production grade environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;M.Sc in Statistics, Computer Science, Mathematics, or a related fie

