&lt;p&gt;You will act as a trusted advisor to GTM leadership, helping them navigate a fast-paced environment, drive organizational changes, and build high-performing teams. This is a highly strategic role that requires a deep understanding of business goals and the ability to translate them into impactful people strategies.&lt;/p&gt;
