&lt;p&gt;- Run the team&#39;s Agile development process, working with Product to set objectives and build a development plan to achieve them&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Own the technical vision and architecture for highly scalable, real-time and batch systems that serve Riskified&#39;s core fraud-analysis offering&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Participate in hands-on development and code review&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Lead the hiring and onboarding of new team members&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- Collaborate closely with research, data science, and product teams to define and implement new features and shape the roadmap&lt;/p&gt;
